OL,3,CGuernsey parishes call for more
OL,4,Crepresentation in central government
OL,6,FParishes are calling for more
OL,7,Frepresentation in central government
OL,8,Fas Guernsey heads to its second Island
OL,9,FWide Election in June.
OL,11,FIt comes as St Martin's Douzaine
OL,12,Fstarted work on a community plan after
OL,13,Fa disagreement on where affordable
OL,14,Fhousing should be built.
OL,16,FGuernsey's douzaines are responsible
OL,17,Ffor plenty, but do they have enough
OL,18,Fpower and representation in central
OL,19,Fgovernment?
