OL,3,CGuernsey parishes call for more
OL,4,Crepresentation in central government
OL,6,FThis is a question that has been
OL,7,Fraised by a recent announcement to
OL,8,Flaunch a community plan in St Martin.
OL,10,FSt Martin Constable, Samantha Bauer
OL,11,Fsaid: "This came about because last
OL,12,Fsummer, the IDP review was to build a
OL,13,Flot of affordable housing on the
OL,14,Fperiphery of the parish.
OL,16,F"It was something they didn't know
OL,17,Fabout in advance and it generated a
OL,18,Flot of concern."
