OL,3,CGuernsey parishes call for more
OL,4,Crepresentation in central government
OL,6,FA similar plan has already been
OL,7,Fdeveloped in St Pierre du Bois,
OL,8,Fbrought ahead by a douzaine to guide
OL,9,Fhow the parish is developed.
OL,11,FWhile the plans cannot force any
OL,12,Fchanges, they are essentially pre-
OL,13,Femptive representations.
OL,15,FGuernsey used to vote in seven
OL,16,Fdeputies by district encompassing all
OL,17,F10 parishes.
