OL,3,CGuernsey parishes call for more
OL,4,Crepresentation in central government
OL,6,FPeople would therefore vote for people
OL,7,Fclose to them geographically so that
OL,8,Fdeputies could represent them on
OL,9,Fimportant parochial issues.
OL,11,FA referendum in 2018 cut this
OL,12,Fconnection by introducing island-wide
OL,13,Fvoting.
OL,15,FNow, islanders can vote for anyone,
OL,16,Fanywhere and it has had several
OL,17,Funintended consequences.
OL,19,FThe shift to island-wide voting saw a
OL,20,Fcollapse in the number of deputies
OL,21,Fvoted in from the northern parishes.
