OL,3,CGuernsey parishes call for more
OL,4,Crepresentation in central government
OL,6,FHowever, in 2016, the northern
OL,7,Fparishes of St Sampson and Vale had 12
OL,8,Fdeputies - this fell by half to only
OL,9,Fsix following the election in 2020.
OL,11,FIn contrast, the southern and western
OL,12,Fparishes increased from 10 deputies in
OL,13,F2016 to 17 deputies in 2020.
OL,15,FDeputies are invited to parish
OL,16,Fmeetings, but the setup is not perfect.
OL,18,FThe impact of the first Island Wide
OL,19,FElection has been realised, and the
OL,20,Fsecond is approaching.
